description: Sandra AI provides an AI-driven receptionist service designed for car dealerships, focusing on automated call management and appointment scheduling available 24/7. The technology integrates with dealership systems to improve operational efficiency and ensure consistent handling of customer calls.

external_description: Sandra AI is revolutionizing customer service in the automotive industry as the first multilingual AI receptionist dedicated to car dealerships. We specialize in providing 24/7, seamless customer interactions, helping dealerships improve efficiency, capture leads, and deliver exceptional service experiences. From scheduling appointments to answering customer inquiries, Sandra AI automates the entire receptionist process, freeing up valuable time for your team. Show more Show less

external_description: Uniti AI is the AI sales agent platform built for global commercial real estate. It automates lead engagement, qualification, and scheduling across multiple channels, helping operators convert more leads and close deals faster. Used in 15+ countries, Uniti AI seamlessly integrates into existing CRMs and PMS—no extra tech required. Designed for all asset classes and languages, its initial focus is on coworking and self-storage. Think of it as hiring a 24/7 sales rep. Backed by top VCs and founded by real estate and AI experts, Uniti AI is building the AI workforce of the future.

description: The main product is a digital retailing platform for automotive dealerships that automates sales and financing processes to enhance efficiency in lead generation and transaction management. It utilizes technologies such as soft credit checks, digital identity verification, and real-time trade-in valuations to minimize fraud risks and streamline operations.

external_description: At Autocorp.ai, we are pioneering the future of the mobility industry by integrating cutting-edge fintech with the latest in E-commerce technology, ID Verification, Lender Intentions and Fraud Prevention solutions. Our mission is to transform the automotive market landscape, offering both consumers and dealerships a seamless, secure, and superior buying and selling journey. By leveraging our deep industry insights and technological expertise, we provide a comprehensive suite of Virtual Retailing Tools & Software designed to streamline the car shopping and buying process. By integrating cutting-edge online financing options, including real time credit data with seamless lender integrations, we ensure a smooth, secure, and efficient digital experience for all users. Our comprehensive suite of services not only enhances operational efficiency for dealers but also revolutionizes the customer journey, making every transaction as transparent and user-friendly as possible. In an era where digital transformation is key, Autocorp.ai stands out by providing a holistic approach to virtual retailing in the automotive sector. Our solutions are crafted to meet the dual needs of fraud prevention and efficient eCommerce transactions, thereby setting new standards in the industry. With a keen focus on integrating real time credit paired with lenders into the digital experience, we facilitate a seamless connection between financing options and consumer needs, ensuring every interaction is optimized for satisfaction and security. This unique blend of technology and service excellence positions Autocorp.ai as a leader in the future of automotive fintech, driving forward with innovation, integrity, and an unwavering commitment to revolutionizing the way the world shops for and purchases vehicles.

description: Mia is an AI-driven phone agent specifically designed for automotive dealerships, capable of managing calls, scheduling appointments, and providing real-time vehicle information around the clock. It utilizes natural language processing and rapid voice response technologies to integrate with existing dealership systems, enhancing customer interactions and operational efficiency.

external_description: Meet Mia, your AI super employee here to answer calls, schedule appointments, and provide instant assistance—turning missed connections into revenue 24/7/365. With human-like response time, Mia fully integrates into any automotive system to check inventory, set appointments, and notify your staff of new leads. Plus, Mia naturally detects customer language and can answer calls in multiple languages, no "press 2" necessary.

Highlights of my role include:

Developing and executing innovative sales strategies to penetrate new markets.

Leading a dynamic team in delivering unparalleled service and AI-driven solutions.

description: QoreAI offers a cloud-based platform tailored for the automotive sector, integrating customer identity verification, document management, and credit reporting into a cohesive system. The platform utilizes open-API architecture and asynchronous messaging to improve operational efficiency and enhance customer engagement within dealerships.

external_description: QoreAI liberates automotive dealerships from fragmented data chaos. We transform scattered information across DMS, CRM, and multiple systems into a single source of truth that empowers confident, data-driven decisions. Unlike traditional marketing services, we focus solely on making your data work for you. Through our specialized platform, we organize, clean, enhance, monitor, and connect your dealership's data, enabling you to finally see your complete customer story and optimize your marketing investments with clarity and confidence. Our mission is simple: Free Your Data. Find Your Truth. We help dealerships: - Unite fragmented customer data across all systems - Transform manual spreadsheet processes into automated insights - Replace data politics with data confidence - Enable AI-powered decision making - Optimize marketing spend through clear performance metrics

description: The product is an AI-driven platform designed for real estate professionals that automates administrative tasks through voice commands, enabling users to capture feedback, organize CRM records, and manage follow-ups. description: The main product is an AI-driven SMS solution specifically designed for the automotive industry, which automates text messaging to enhance customer service and engagement. It utilizes trained AI models for both inbound and outbound communications and integrates with existing CRM systems.

external_description: ICOM AI is a cutting-edge SaaS company that provides an AI-powered texting platform for the automotive retail industry. Our specialized natural language processing technology is designed to efficiently and effectively communicate with automotive leads and customers, revolutionizing the way auto dealerships and auto tech companies interact with their customers. Our mission is to bring the most advanced conversational AI products and support to automotive retail, and we are dedicated to enhancing the customer experience for both auto dealerships and software companies. With features like acquisition lead management, outbound SMS campaigns, and after-hours support, ICOM AI is committed to helping our clients achieve their sales goals and exceed their customers' expectations. Join us on our mission to transform customer interactions in automotive retail with advanced conversational AI technology. WWW.ICOM.AI

description: Otom.ai offers a sales enablement platform that leverages artificial intelligence to enhance sales productivity by integrating data from CRM systems, call recordings, and emails. Its key functionalities include generating meeting summaries, providing deal dashboards, and an inquiry tool that analyzes various data sources to yield actionable insights for sales teams.

description: AutoAcquire AI is a software platform designed to automate the used car acquisition process for dealerships, utilizing AI to identify and source vehicles from registered owners within targeted geographic areas. The platform features technologies such as remote inspections, custom instant offers, and transportation management to enhance inventory efficiency and profitability.

description: ALOMA offers a platform that enables developers to automate workflows through custom JavaScript logic, APIs, and Webhooks, allowing for seamless integration with various applications. Its dynamic automation technology adapts in real-time to data changes and includes built-in error correction to enhance the integration process.

external_description: Building AI-powered generative process automation for operations teams to automate any process across any application on the fly. Contact us to find out how a customer was able to integrate 7 apps with less than 80% of the effort they estimated was required to code the integration themselves. Aloma reduces integration to 3 simple steps: 1. Connect to Aloma - no pre-processing or processing of data required 2. Aloma dynamically processes your data - selecting which transformations to make in real time based on your rules and requirements 3. Automatically writes data to the required apps - Aloma send the right data to the right app and can execute commands as required Unlike other integration tools with standard "fixed" integrations designed for business users, Aloma is built for developers and provides the power and flexibility of code with developer user experience. Founded in 2022, our mission is to enable companies to get more done in less time. Get in touch today for a demo and find out how you can accelerate your integrations: hello@aloma.io

Powered by AI, we enable operations teams to automate any process across any app.

Most operations leaders are challenged today to automate workflows due to the sheer number of apps their teams are using. Automating a process now means building and maintaining a web of complex integrations that need updating every time a new app is introduced or business conditions change. 

Aloma simplifies this by capturing your business logic and generating a new automation in real time for each workflow task received. This automation is based on your current process logic and automatically adapts integration to ensure automation success.  

You can now focus on scaling your automated operations instead of having to choose between adding IT expense to automate a process or adding people for manual operations.

Our vision is to allow a business leader to independently manage a fully automated operation. We are leveraging AI to generate automatons based on business processes that can adapt to change and new apps. description: The primary offering is an automotive marketing platform that leverages machine learning to analyze customer data, generate personalized vehicle upgrade proposals, and predict future purchases based on trade-in values and current inventory. It integrates with dealership systems for real-time updates on customer records and sales transactions, while also incorporating OEM incentives to enhance the accuracy of the generated offers.

external_description: Trata is an AI-powered omnichannel communication co-worker designed specifically for auto services. Our AI models are trained on automotive workflows, ensuring they understand your unique needs—whether it’s booking appointments, managing inbound and outbound calls, or following up on service inquiries. With Trata, your business stays responsive 24/7, handling everything from customer queries to appointment reminders and beyond. By automating routine interactions and streamlining workflows, Trata helps you focus on what matters most—delivering top-notch service to your customers. It's not just AI; it’s an intelligent partner for your team, built to keep your operations running smoothly and your customers satisfied.

description: MotoAcquire provides a platform for vehicle acquisition that features instant valuations, firm offers based on vehicle condition, and monthly updates on vehicle value. The technology includes a dealer portal for managing acquisitions, automated text messaging for customer engagement, and integration with existing CRM systems to improve operational efficiency.

external_description: We build automotive software that dealers and consumers truly want to use. At MotoAcquire, we help modern dealerships acquire more vehicles from consumers by combining value tracking, high-converting website funnels, and creator-powered lead generation. Today’s customers expect fast, personalized, and modern digital experiences. We give dealers the tools to meet that expectation — while generating more trade-ins, increasing gross, and staying top-of-mind across the entire ownership cycle. Our platform includes four tightly integrated products: 🚗 MotoConvert – Instantly engage customers on your website with a quick trade-in valuation, value tracking enrollment, and firm offer requests. A beautiful widget that can replace your current tools or enhance them. 📬 MotoRetain – Stay connected with past customers through monthly, personalized vehicle value emails. It’s effortless marketing that adds real value and re-engages your database with perfect timing. 📱 MotoSocial – Empower your sales team on social with link-in-bio experiences that drive real actions — valuations, value tracking, firm offers — all tied to their name and store. 🎯 MotoLeads – Partner with automotive creators and influencers to generate high-intent leads. These aren’t just third-party leads — they’re trusted referrals with better close rates and buyer signals. We believe good software should feel modern, be fun to use, and fit into a dealership’s workflow — not fight against it. If you’re trying to buy more cars from consumers, stay relevant in the social era, or give customers a reason to come back — MotoAcquire was built for you.

Our platform includes four tightly integrated products:

🚗 MotoConvert – Instantly engage customers on your website with a quick trade-in valuation, value tracking enrollment, and firm offer requests. A beautiful widget that can replace your current tools or enhance them.

📬 MotoRetain – Stay connected with past customers through monthly, personalized vehicle value emails. It’s effortless marketing that adds real value and re-engages your database with perfect timing.

📱 MotoSocial – Empower your sales team on social with link-in-bio experiences that drive real actions — valuations, value tracking, firm offers — all tied to their name and store.

🎯 MotoLeads – Partner with automotive creators and influencers to generate high-intent leads. These aren’t just third-party leads — they’re trusted referrals with better close rates and buyer signals.

We believe good software should feel modern, be fun to use, and fit into a dealership’s workflow — not fight against it.
